snippet.title: Celebrities DEFENDING Johnny Depp against Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Celebrities DEFENDING Johnny Depp against Amber Heard. 
In recent times, the news has had no scarcity of stories surrounding Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's marriage scandal. Following the failure of Johnny's libel suit, multiple celebrities who have known and worked with the "Jack Sparrow" actor over the years have jumped to the defense of his character and personality, showing support and solidarity in the face of the allegations leveled against him. 

From long-time friends and fans to colleagues and previous romantic partners, nearly everyone had one glowing review or the other to give, which is why today we would be taking a look at all the celebrities who have defended Johnny Depp against Amber Heard. Make sure to stick around till the end so you don't miss out on any details!
